  "name": {
    "en": "Ultimate Zigbee Hub"
  },
  "description": {
    "en": "Ultimate Zigbee Hub - Professional device categorization system with 1500+ compatible devices. Organized by device function: Motion Detection, Contact Security, Smart Lighting, Power Control, Climate Monitoring, Safety Detection, and Automation Control. Users select devices by what they DO, not by brand. Universal compatibility across all manufacturers. SDK3 compliant with local Zigbee 3.0 operation and no cloud dependencies."
  },
